Package: scrnaVis
Title: Providing beautiful single-cell visualization figtures
Version: 0.0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given="Xiong", family="Yangjie", email="xiongyangjie2020@sibs.ac.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    This package can simply run base seurat pipeline from Seurat object to TSNE or UMAP.
    You can define and draw beautiful figtures by yourself interactively using with web pages by shiny.
